# Build and Run

Preferred flow is Docker-only. Avoid npm helper scripts.

- Build multi-stage image:
  - `docker build -t alexschladetsch/cone-counter:latest .`
- Run (production):
  - `docker-compose up -d`
  - Or: `docker run -d -p 3000:3000 -v cone-data:/app/data alexschladetsch/cone-counter:latest`
- Image serves:
  - API: `http://<host>:3000/api/*`
  - Frontend: `http://<host>:3000/`
- Healthcheck: `GET /api/stats` returns 200 when up
- Persistent data is stored at `/app/data` inside container (SQLite file `cones.db`).